rows.label: qst201710_msg0002
rows.name: Looks like we reached the goal.

rows.label: qst201710_msg0004
rows.name:
Yes, Your Majesty!
But h-how do you know who I am?

rows.label: qst201710_msg0005
rows.name:
A little bird told me. I hear you are
rather a loose cannon, though powerful.

rows.label: qst201710_msg0006
rows.name:
Th-thank you very much!
I'm honored, Your Majesty!

rows.label: qst201710_msg0007
rows.name:
...I'm not sure that was as much
of a compliment as you think.

rows.label: qst201710_msg0008
rows.name:
That you could so easily penetrate
our defenses...

rows.label: qst201710_msg0009
rows.name:
I must confess that, as the ruler of the
Empire, I have mixed feelings about it.

rows.label: qst201710_msg0011
rows.name:
The Superbian soldiers
were no pushovers.

rows.label: qst201710_msg0013
rows.name:
I shall take your word for it
and fret no more.
